{"tid":2352337,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"西環集中營︰DQ居港權勢加劇移民潮（季陶）","createTime":"2021-01-04T03:30:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T04:17:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7cf983a049cd8933b0f2da1acbd54bc578f0865c","tid":2352337,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T03:30:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210104/LPBXKHBDMRF3LN2X773V6HPT7Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210104%2FLPBXKHBDMRF3LN2X773V6HPT7Y%2F&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZyXdT8yuj5BXRLHKnqfTXFLo%3D&h=f0571167\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210104%2FLPBXKHBDMRF3LN2X773V6HPT7Y%2F&h=64cbd146\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210104/LPBXKHBDMRF3LN2X773V6HPT7Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n西環集中營︰DQ居港權勢加劇移民潮（季陶）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/KX8ByUhVKvn_4df9a2D5zNPcEyY=/6720x4480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Q3W2DU52IVA4BA7MOGS27SFDWU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKX8ByUhVKvn_4df9a2D5zNPcEyY%3D%2F6720x4480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQ3W2DU52IVA4BA7MOGS27SFDWU.jpg&h=0bb9b66e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■因港版國安法而引發的移民潮今年才會浮面，對香港經濟會做成多大影響，仍是未知數。<br />\n<br />\n踏入2021年，不少專家評論今年經濟社會狀況，均如季陶之說，香港失業及企業結業潮恐成新一年重要問題。有專業人士均稱，新一年另一問題將是移民潮，坦言因港版國安法而引發的移民潮今年才會浮面，對香港經濟會做成多大影響，仍是未知數，他更指即使北京在雙重國籍問題上出招，恐怕也難改變決定移民的港人想法，「因為今次移民潮同97年嗰次好唔同，嗰次好多人仲諗住回流返香港搵錢，但今次好多人一走，就諗住以後唔返香港。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：袁國勇揭3%樣本無人類DNA  水喉水扮唾液 檢測者作弊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港人已不介意無法回流<br />\n<br />\n該名專業人士早在1997年前已移民再回流香港，他說單是1月份，「排滿晒同朋友、同事、下屬嘅送行宴，個個plan晒1、2月走」，而最多人去的地方仍是英國，「即使英國疫情嚴峻，好多仲一家大細堅持走，怕遲咗情況有變」，他直言BNO的5+1方案1月底可申請，相信1月後走的人會更多，「有啲嘢唔係你北京、林鄭話冇移民潮就冇，真係冇人走去英國，李嘉誠會投資10億英鎊喺英國起樓？愛國愛港嘅有線老細邱達昌，會喺曼城係咁起樓？冇需求佢哋會投資咩？你信地產商定政府？」<br />\n<br />\n至於建制陣營不斷放風指北京會針對BNO的5+1方案，在雙重國籍問題上出招，該專業人士作為回流過來人，坦言。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：醫護工會轟林鄭「後面放火」<br />\n季陶<br />\n<br />\n周一及周五刊出"},{"pid":"c25054ddbb8ea2bb85cf3a6f16f3e59333be0ae5","tid":2352337,"uid":13503,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T03:34:07.000Z","msg":"信超人好過信政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />超人撤資大陸唔夠幾年就樓巿大跌，依家超人去英國又係另一個啓示<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48445e1463d16df610e07f7aba59afca8d6b9b19","tid":2352337,"uid":8105,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T03:44:20.000Z","msg":"FG 都打算今年內走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搵翻十零二十萬就拜拜你條尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f629561b3f99e2677401e7dd2aa691129aca609","tid":2352337,"uid":152705,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c25054ddbb8ea2bb85cf3a6f16f3e59333be0ae5","tid":2352337,"uid":13503,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T03:34:07.000Z","msg":"信超人好過信政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />超人撤資大陸唔夠幾年就樓巿大跌，依家超人去英國又係另一個啓示<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T04:00:45.000Z","msg":"一早五眼同誠哥已經俾晒signal , 繼續選擇留港嘅 good luck <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3325d532db65ecc96369e18eb8adc15b61890e46","tid":2352337,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T04:03:01.000Z","msg":"agree不介意"},{"pid":"ff6306006ac7cce755fbc4bb0f555112e1cb5337","tid":2352337,"uid":267283,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T04:16:09.000Z","msg":"無錢 無專業嘅<br />\n都打算去英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0669941f45b9cc4fa175ab4c8e37beec7ab20fa","tid":2352337,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime